      h1.ui.header.center.aligned How Data4America is Funded
      p Data4America is fortunate to enjoy the support from a growing group of donors around the world.
      p Our donors support 100% of our content, editorial, and event operations. Our funders support us because they believe the same thing we do: There is too much noise in politics. Policy education powered by data science and data visualization can help solve it.
      p We maintain a strict firewall between editorial and funding. As a non-partisan group, the principle of 'ideas over politics' guides us.
